Description: WHS SEEKS TO PROVIDE TRANSPORTATION BETWEEN THE MARK CENTER, THE PENTAGON RESERVATION, AND THE CITY OF ALEXANDRIA, VA FOR ITS EMPLOYEES. THESE SERVICES WILL BE AWARDED TO THE CITY OF ALEXANDRIA (102 ROUTE-DASH) AND THE WASHINGTON METROPOLITAN AREA TRANSIT AUTHORITY (7M ROUTE).
